"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:40:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半年前, 26歲, d 粒粒印仲未褪色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係半年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個陣睇完西醫有無睇中醫？"},{"pid":"97d0967f079382a40099cbd73b99c5454563f0e8","tid":247144,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"十三歲生咗一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93ec1c41d447f868ccfcba0c42799e6e3e2b81f","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十三歲生咗一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個排係咪好夜訓？"},{"pid":"5770990ef358cad459c19f69767c4fd51e3d0509","tid":247144,"uid":27669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"中四定中五生過係腰，<br />\n依架過咗四五年都無乜事，但有黑色印同有時會好痕<br />\n<br />\n唔知係乾燥定關生過蛇事"},{"pid":"66a577e3d6ceb19d986c524e3f583a6b7ce9c095","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中四定中五生過係腰，<br />\n依架過咗四五年都無乜事，但有黑色印同有時會好痕<br />\n<br />\n唔知係乾燥定關生過蛇事</blockquote><br />\n你後來有無話改變左生活習慣咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我到而家都仲有個疤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83675ae899f4d677dc1539b5bb71a080334863c","tid":247144,"uid":16067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>半年前, 26歲, d 粒粒印仲未褪色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係半年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個陣睇完西醫有無睇中醫？</blockquote><br />\n無用, 打返支疫苗最實際, 不過醫生話支針要50歲先打得, on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d36188265c78dc336ed5ae4497c319d60cd1c14","tid":247144,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:45:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十三歲生咗一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個排係咪好夜訓？</blockquote><br />\n又冇喎，不過天生免疫力差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d37d5347c45e606846d741570eda870106be759","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>半年前, 26歲, d 粒粒印仲未褪色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係半年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個陣睇完西醫有無睇中醫？</blockquote><br />\n無用, 打返支疫苗最實際, 不過醫生話支針要50歲先打得, on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好驚復發，經常提心吊膽"},{"pid":"55f6d452d0fac58d93f1b51f772f8fe23e20f04e","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十三歲生咗一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個排係咪好夜訓？</blockquote><br />\n又冇喎，不過天生免疫力差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？"},{"pid":"ee448fe1dd0a3818716951be950ba9963f63a582","tid":247144,"uid":55055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生完就冇咩野<br />\n不過生蛇個位會有一粒粒既野 <br />\n應該會跟成世</blockquote><br />\n有個疤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問你會唔會一夜訓就覺得唔舒服？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生完應該唔會再痛嫁啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活習慣冇變<br />\n係個排大壓力先會生<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"481f597d66862f4f07f217d8d2d3b70f6e6cabdc","tid":247144,"uid":20494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生蛇之後生活習慣如何？<br />\n仲有無神經痛？<br />\n而家只要一夜訓兼壓力大就好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩年前生過。但係生前生後都唔痛。睇寶血無用，之後去st.  paul睇都係無用，再之後同事介紹個西醫食左幾日藥就好番晒lu"},{"pid":"1edf199b463308829728a059a207526af07f8d73","tid":247144,"uid":16067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生完就冇咩野<br />\n不過生蛇個位會有一粒粒既野 <br />\n應該會跟成世</blockquote><br />\n有個疤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問你會唔會一夜訓就覺得唔舒服？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生完應該唔會再痛嫁啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活習慣冇變<br />\n係個排大壓力先會生<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n我個時完左甩晒焦仲好似有針吉咁, 醫生話正常, 好彩我後生, d 老人家會吉幾年"},{"pid":"e33aa68989fa5068908bb03d9edd3e60477ece66","tid":247144,"uid":78443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"睇HA<br />\n醫生開番d antiviral 食幾個星期 就好哂"},{"pid":"08e5aaab98bfdc9d85a22d22c217dfa06c0cc46d","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生完就冇咩野<br />\n不過生蛇個位會有一粒粒既野 <br />\n應該會跟成世</blockquote><br />\n有個疤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問你會唔會一夜訓就覺得唔舒服？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生完應該唔會再痛嫁啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活習慣冇變<br />\n係個排大壓力先會生<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n佢好似會陣痛陣痛咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家盡量叫自己咪咁大壓力<br />\n但係仲會好驚又生<br />\n個一次諗住係暗瘡<br />\n點知痛到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047c0b702731bc7c0e65c1a8ddf895737ac48713","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生蛇之後生活習慣如何？<br />\n仲有無神經痛？<br />\n而家只要一夜訓兼壓力大就好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩年前生過。但係生前生後都唔痛。睇寶血無用，之後去st.  paul睇都係無用，再之後同事介紹個西醫食左幾日藥就好番晒lu</blockquote><br />\n內服？有無外敷？<br />\n記得個陣食藍色藥食到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c94cf6abd5e8e88b5e7c502b4864206ccc2a2e0","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:54:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>生完就冇咩野<br />\n不過生蛇個位會有一粒粒既野 <br />\n應該會跟成世</blockquote><br />\n有個疤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想問你會唔會一夜訓就覺得唔舒服？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生完應該唔會再痛嫁啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活習慣冇變<br />\n係個排大壓力先會生<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n我個時完左甩晒焦仲好似有針吉咁, 醫生話正常, 好彩我後生, d 老人家會吉幾年</blockquote><br />\n我而家都硬係仍住個位置唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd27eab1c683758a3ae5e56fac6e9c9f2b56ef6b","tid":247144,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:55:07.000Z","msg":"生完蛇之後幾年都冇復發過<br />\n之後都冇特別去戒口或者早訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd 印有淡色左嘅 唔留心望就唔覺"},{"pid":"d04cd81ea890074fce8fb14b169da66eec793385","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:55:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇HA<br />\n醫生開番d antiviral 食幾個星期 就好哂</blockquote><br />\n個陣食左三星期藥 食到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19986cc39960b087653b2a70bf213728d921e793","tid":247144,"uid":11381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"小學試過 背脊有一撻野+好似俾火燒同針吉咁<br />\n好返之後而家冇印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fd69fa67776