 />\n我個陣食個劑量少，食三次已經好辛苦<br />\n後來先話食得太少，就一日五次<br />\n諗到個隻藥個胃都唔舒服"},{"pid":"0b3f430e043e0761ded0f03507d8a1bbdea47df4","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇HA<br />\n醫生開番d antiviral 食幾個星期 就好哂</blockquote><br />\n個陣食左三星期藥 食到想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個陣主要搽藥膏 同吞藥丸</blockquote><br />\n一樣<br />\n諗起都怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c759207329701b80c840ce63df948bfc9f9a31","tid":247144,"uid":12433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"我15歲嗰陣係英國生，之後去咗睇急症然後食咗d唔知咩藥（唔記得咗）等咗個幾月好返曬連印都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31562ba9a2f056ba4f4797cbd5da93c1f39ae90f","tid":247144,"uid":117384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"17歲個年生過係頸 <br />\n之後搞到面癱左半年"},{"pid":"34840c03548616be3220ebc672d7b557d368ebb5","tid":247144,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生完蛇之後幾年都冇復發過<br />\n之後都冇特別去戒口或者早訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd 印有淡色左嘅 唔留心望就唔覺</blockquote><br />\n最好咪復發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排一chur就好驚<br />\n最慘我生係好顯眼位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個陣生係腹肌位置再落側腰然後繼續向橫延伸到背脊 淨係右邊身有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc480acb817b6dae831b1a2ecd010324bfbd0f1","tid":247144,"uid":16067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"btw, 我係生係腳, 春袋隔離大髀伸到小腿, 幾驚禍及JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb1a25b5b2a990c99a894c68dec1e14a518838f","tid":247144,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited