3c5ee86fd37414dfca","tid":247144,"uid":65974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上兩個月生完 依家仲會痛同一攰得制就想復發咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生完之後身體好差 啲西藥好勁 上次仲入埋廠</blockquote><br />\n你明白我想講咩！！！<br />\n就係有一種隱隱地嘅神經痛<br />\n一chur就好驚又生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntake care 真心"},{"pid":"4d4f8a6c19e170976751129ec148644bf220249a","tid":247144,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T15:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上兩個月生完 依家仲會痛同一攰得制就想復發咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生完之後身體好差 啲西藥好勁 上次仲入埋廠</blockquote><br />\n你明白我想講咩！！！<br />\n就係有一種隱隱地嘅神經痛<br />\n一chur就好驚又生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntake care 真心</blockquote><br />\n我明 搞到我痴痴地線咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時超攰 第二朝訓醒突然痛 我係生係肋骨去到背隻<br />\n之後一痛就覺得會復發 <br />\n個腦就會諗死啦好驚啊點算 愈諗愈痛<br />\n情緒唔好都會痛 <br />\n但我都係咁夜訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依幾日都有痛"}]}